Package org.sakaiproject.localization.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContentProperties
    This class should be configured as a "Content" bundles bean (see components.xml) in order to provide the context for the kernel to load the localized content_*.properties files.
    ContentTypeProperties
    This class should be configured as a "content_type" bundles bean (see components.xml) in order to provide the context for the kernel to load the localized content_type_*.properties files.
    EmailImplProperties
    This class should be configured as a "Email-impl" bundles bean (see components.xml) in order to provide the context for the kernel to load the localized email-impl_*.properties files.
    SiteemaconProperties
    This class should be configured as a "Siteemacon" bundles bean (see components.xml) in order to provide the context for the kernel to load the localized siteemacon_*.properties files.
    SiteImplProperties
    This class should be configured as a "SiteImpl" bundles bean (see components.xml) in order to provide the context for the kernel to load the localized tools*.properties files.
    ToolProperties
    This class should be configured as a "Tool" bundles bean (see components.xml) in order to provide the context for the kernel to load the localized tools*.properties files.
    TypeProperties
    This class should be configured as a "types" bundles bean (see components.xml) in order to provide the context for the kernel to load the localized types_*.properties files.
